import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { NgForm } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-login', templateUrl: './login.component.html', styleUrls: ['./login.component.css'] }) export class LoginComponent { email: string = ''; password: string = ''; login(loginForm: NgForm) { if (loginForm.valid) { if (this.email === 'test@example.com' && this.password === 'password') { console.log('Login successful'); } else { console.log('Invalid credentials'); } } } }

Login

Email is required.
Invalid email format.
Password is required.
Password should be at least 6 characters long.
